<sidebyside width="35%"><image source="images/hp8-3-31.png"><description>inclined plane</description></image></sidebyside>
<ol label="a">
<li>How long, to the nearest 0.01 second, will it take the ball to roll 2 feet horizontally on a plane tilted by <m>12\degree</m>?</li>
