 <exercise number="59"><statement><m>y=\dfrac{\csc x}{\cot x}</m></statement>
<answer><m>\dfrac{\csc x}{\cot x}=\dfrac{\dfrac{1}{\sin x}}{\dfrac{\cos x}{\sin x}} = \dfrac{1}{\sin x}\div \dfrac{\cos x}{\sin x}=\dfrac{1}{\sin x}\cdot \dfrac{\sin x}{\cos x} = \dfrac{1}{\cos x} = \sec x</m></answer></exercise>
 
