<exercise number="93"><statement><p>Write each of the other five trig functions in terms of <m>\sin t</m> only.</p></statement>
<answer><m>\cos t = \pm \sqrt{1-\sin^2 t},~\tan t = \dfrac{\pm \sin t}{\sqrt{1-\sin^2 t}},~\sec t = \dfrac{\pm 1}{\sqrt{1-\sin^2 t}},</m><m>\csc t = \dfrac{1}{\sin t},~ \cot t = \dfrac{\pm \sqrt{1-\sin^2 t}}{\sin t}</m></answer></exercise>

